"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1897765-Team-GB-Noah-Williams-Olympic-Games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Noah Williams wants to honour the memory of the coach who ignited his Olympic dreams by securing a medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999986889634, \"rank\": 1.311027496454781e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diver from Hackney finished 27th on his Olympic debut in Tokyo, missing out on a semi-final attempt, and later sent a message to his followers onInstagramwhich read: \\\"Thank you for all the support, I am sorry I could not do you proud x\\\".\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\", \"score\": 0.9999493981328889, \"rank\": 3.60358365697151e-05, \"text\": \"Hackney\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Hackney\"}, {\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6303616751914425, \"rank\": 0.5862055015566463, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But performances in the pool were soon placed firmly into perspective after the death of his much-loved coach Dave Jenkins in October 2021.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.9999986764809937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dave Jenkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jenkins_(musician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old's life was turned upside down and he considered retiring from the sport he loved.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of this (Olympic) cycle is done in his memory,\\\" Williams said.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to quit after he passed.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard when someone passes who is your main motivator, he was training me for events.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really did not enjoy diving after that.\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It still would have been completely different if he just quit, diving would be different, but because he did pass away, it was a lot to process.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the first time in my life that I'd had anything like that to deal with.\\\"\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jenkins was a mentor and a friend to Williams, who had been his coach's prot\\u00e9g\\u00e9 since the age of 16 at London Aquatics Centre.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Aquatics Centre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Aquatics_Centre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after taking time to process the grief, a switch flicked and he was all of a sudden embarking on a second Olympic quest.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I stuck through it and I ended up thinking the opposite, that I could not quit because I wanted to do something in his memory,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not know what else to do apart from dive.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not leave it on Tokyo so hopefully I can do well in Paris for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6303616751914425, \"rank\": 0.5862055015566463, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999986889634, \"rank\": 1.311027496454781e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - this is vital for their pathway to the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been selected alongside Team GB mainstay Tom Daley, approaching his fifth Games, in the men's 10m synchro event for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999959798677854, \"rank\": 4.01980239048273e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1922, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0074540620849596e-53, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.45132049253323e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They secured a quota spot with World Championships silver in Doha earlier this year, their first international competition as a pair, and Daley will now go for a golden title defence in France having triumphed alongside Matty Lee in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.6225451842160994e-12, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}, {\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9188629261582981, \"rank\": 0.08157405141126706, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6303616751914425, \"rank\": 0.5862055015566463, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think people realise how good Tom is,\\\" Williams said.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no one else in the world who could have two years out, come back and be a world medallist and world champion in the team event.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's insanely hard-working and talented, he's miles above everyone else.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Anything can happen on the day and we have done really well this year so I hope I can help him out.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Individually it's quite lonely, synchro is the closest we can get to a team sport and it's a lot more enjoyable, sharing the whole event with someone,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You get to share the pressure, it does not feel as daunting, especially when it's Tom.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get to just be there so I like it so far.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tom is a massive name and the pressure is on him - that's good for me and how I compete.\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At that first Olympics, I had to wait until the last day to compete so it was literally just me and Tom.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I knew he was going to do really well and I put a lot of expectation on myself and it did not work.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have learned a lot from it and I have come back stronger.\\\"\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3532, \"end\": 3548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999996589395, \"rank\": 3.409907926038173e-10, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Find out how your numbers make amazing happen at: www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk #TNLAthletes #MakeAmazingHappen  SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3919, \"end\": 3932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1070552488428675e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 4020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3968, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1070552488428675e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"